lead_paragraph: A bystander was killed in Sao Paulo on Sunday after being hit in the chest by a bullet fired as Palmeiras and Corinthians fans battled ahead of the Paulista state championship derby game.

headline.print_headline: Bystander Killed as Corinthians, Palmeiras Fans Battle
